<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About | Christmas Gift Inventory</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar', {links: links}) %>

    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="page-title"><%= title %></h1>
    </header>

    <main class="about-main">
      <section class="about-section mission">
        <h2 class="section-title">Mission</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          This website is designed to simplify the process of managing donations
          and distributing Christmas gifts to children in need. It serves as an
          inventory application, helping organizations and volunteers
          efficiently track and organize gift items, ensuring that every child
          receives a thoughtful present this holiday season.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section features">
        <h2 class="section-title">Features of the Application</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li class="feature-item">
            Track donated gifts with detailed descriptions, prices, and
            categories.
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            Organize gifts into age-appropriate groups to ensure suitability.
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            Maintain an up-to-date inventory using dynamic data from a database.
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            Sort by users and ensure user validation for updating or deleting.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section involvement">
        <h2 class="section-title">Get Involved</h2>
        <p class="section-text">
          Whether you wish to donate gifts or assist in the distribution
          process, this application makes it easy to contribute. Explore our
          <a href="/donate" class="donate-link">Donate</a> page to learn more
          about how you can help make this Christmas special for children in
          need.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
